I've been on this server for about 3 years... Joined when it used to be called MCZone. Now Avicus. OCN was my first server ever... my Mother-Server. I personally prefer Avicus because the community here is much more tightly-knit and close.

We're gonna get a huge META soon that will introduce a slur of new content and whatnot. Perhaps if you're willing you could stay for awhile until we get it?
